# Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) README

This repository contains a collection of Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) for various DevOps tasks and technologies. Each SOP provides detailed instructions for installation, configuration, and usage of specific tools or services.

## SOPs List

1. *Ansible Installation and SSH Connectivity*
   - Instructions for installing Ansible and establishing SSH connectivity.

2. *Docker and Minikube on Ubuntu*
   - Steps to install Docker and Minikube for local Kubernetes development on Ubuntu.

3. *Grafana Installing and Creating as Service*
   - Guidance for installing Grafana and configuring it as a service for monitoring.

4. *Grafana-AWS Linux AMI*
   - Instructions specific to installing Grafana on an AWS Linux AMI instance.

5. *Jenkins-AWS Ubuntu*
   - SOP for setting up Jenkins on an AWS Ubuntu instance.

6. *Jenkins - Email Server Configuration*
   - Configuring Jenkins to send emails for notifications and alerts.

7. *Jenkins-AWS Linux*
   - Installation steps for Jenkins on an AWS Linux instance.

8. *Jenkins-GitHub Integration-Using SSH*
   - Integrating Jenkins with GitHub using SSH for source code management.

9. *Jenkins-Master-Slave Architecture*
   - Guidelines for setting up a Jenkins master-slave architecture for distributed builds.

10. *Kubernetes Installation*
    - SOP for installing Kubernetes for container orchestration.

11. *Maven-AWS Linux AMI*
    - Maven installation instructions specific to AWS Linux AMI.

12. *Node Exporter Installation SOP*
    - Installing and configuring Node Exporter for Prometheus monitoring.

13. *Prometheus - AWS Linux EC2*
    - Installing Prometheus for monitoring on an AWS Linux EC2 instance.

14. *Prometheus - Installing and Configuring*
    - General instructions for installing and configuring Prometheus monitoring.

15. *SonarQube on AWS EC2*
    - Installation steps for SonarQube on an AWS EC2 instance.

16. *Terraform on Amazon Linux 5.10 EC2 Instance*
    - SOP for installing Terraform on an Amazon Linux EC2 instance.

17. *Terraform-AWS EC2*
    - Instructions for using Terraform to provision AWS EC2 instances.

18. *WordPress in a Docker container on AWS*
    - Deploying WordPress in a Docker container on AWS.

19. *nginx webserver on AWS EC2*
    - Setting up an nginx web server on an AWS EC2 instance.

20. *tomcat - AWS Linux AMI*
    - Installing and configuring Apache Tomcat on an AWS Linux AMI.

## Usage
Each SOP provides detailed instructions for specific tasks or technologies. Follow the steps outlined in each SOP to achieve the desired outcome.

## Contribution
Contributions to improve existing SOPs or add new ones are welcome. Please follow the contribution guidelines outlined in CONTRIBUTING.md.

